flowchart TD

    A[Start Chat] --> B[Ask Budget]


    B --> C{Valid number?}
        C -- No --> B1[Explain expected number<br/>Ask again]
        C -- Yes --> C2{Budget >= $300?}
        C2 -- No --> B2[Warn budget too low<br/>Ask again]
        C2 -- Yes --> D[Ask Use Case]

    D --> E{Recognized use case?}
        E -- No --> D1[Show valid options<br/>Ask again]
        E -- Yes --> E2{Gaming + Low Budget?}
        E2 -- Yes --> E3[Warn about gaming costs]
        E2 -- No --> F[Ask Portability]

    E3 --> F

    F --> G{Valid portability?}
        G -- No --> F1[Explain options<br/>Ask again]
        G -- Yes --> H[Ask OS Preference]

    H --> I{Valid OS?}
        I -- No --> H1[Explain options<br/>Ask again]
        I -- Yes --> J[Compute Recommendation]

    J --> K[Show Specs + Notes]

    K --> L{User input}
        L -- why --> M[Explain Reasoning]
        L -- restart --> B
        L -- other --> K

%% Global commands

    X((help)) --> Y[Show Help Info]
        Y --> L


    Z((restart)) --> B
